{"title":"腾讯云无法使用root登陆服务器","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.045Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/腾讯云无法使用root登陆服务器","updated":"2023-07-28T09:19:24.997Z","content":"<p>前一阵发现自己的腾讯云服务器root登陆总是无法连接，后台多次修改密码也不管用，每次都只能用ubuntu登陆，很不方便。<br>\n在服务器上修改一下配置文件即可。<br>\n首先用普通账号登陆</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/31f387a3d39a4e6b820328be6dafd082.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#取消这两行代码的注释</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">Port 22</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#改成yes</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">PermitRootLogin <span class=\"built_in\">yes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>修改完后按下<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>，保存退出即可</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#重启一下ssh服务</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo systemctl restart sshd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此时用root账户即可登陆服务器！</p>\n","prev":{"title":"研究生学术英语写作网课答案","link":"2023/07/28/研究生学术英语写作网课答案"},"next":{"title":"两台linux服务器配置远程免密登陆","link":"2023/07/28/两台linux服务器配置远程免密登陆"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/腾讯云无法使用root登陆服务器/","reading_time":"157 字约 1 分钟"}